About.

Hi! I’m Bonjovi Jasz V. Fojas, a hard-working Web Developer with a capability to give creative solutions in the least amount of time.  I’ve developed an E-commerce, Product Catalogs, Online Project Management, E-Learning Management System, Leads Generation and Dynamic Eye-catching Websites.

KEEP MOVING FORWARD

Challenges did not stop when I graduated from college, actually, it is just the beginning.  As a matter of fact, challenges are the reason why am I still keep going. It keeps me in shape, competitive and motivated. Every day I challenge myself to overcome my limits to make me a better me. It makes my life interesting and overcoming those is what makes my life meaningful. I used my errors and mistakes as a stepping stone to success. They say forget about the past and failures in order to succeed, I say do not forget about them and learn from it.  Success is a never-ending path and in order to keep up, I keep moving forward.

Way of Work.

QUALITY WEBSITE MATTERS

A common mistake by the most of the people is they think that simply creating a website will easily attract visitors and achieve their goals. But that’s not how it works. “You don’t just build a website, you build a website that sells”.
-Dr. Christopher Dayagdag,
01. PLANNING

A thorough analysis of the project, set purpose and objectives, define the target audience, content distribution strategy,  determine the structure and layout presentation.

02. IMPLEMENTATION

Follow the guidelines from the planning stage, propose an alternative solution to solve the problem, make use of the content to fit the target audience, create an eye-catching website design considering the user experience.

03. COMPLETION

Make sure all objectives are achieved, do a content run-through, quality check the whole project, perform a cross-platform and cross-browser test, act as a visitor.
